09:05.044 --> 09:06.420
<i>♪ See you walkin' round ♪</i>

09:06.504 --> 09:08.548
<i>♪ Like it's a funeral ♪</i>

09:09.173 --> 09:10.716
<i>♪ Not so serious, girl ♪</i>

09:10.800 --> 09:12.843
<i>♪ Why those feet cold? ♪</i>

09:12.927 --> 09:17.348
