09:48.462 --> 09:51.048
<i>♪ I keep on hopin'</i>
<i>We'll eat cake by the ocean ♪</i>

09:51.132 --> 09:53.259
<i>-♪ Ah</i>
<i>-♪ Walk for me, baby ♪</i>

