<i>♪ Let's lose our minds</i>
<i>And go crazy-crazy ♪</i>

10:00.891 --> 10:03.269
Yo, what is that?

10:03.644 --> 10:05.354
Whatever it is, bro...

10:05.438 --> 10:06.647
it's not from Malibu.

10:06.731 --> 10:08.274
<i>♪ Chocolate in my life ♪</i>

10:08.357 --> 10:12.069
<i>♪ Confetti, I'm ready</i>
<i>I need it every night ♪</i>

10:12.528 --> 10:14.447
<i>♪ Red velvet, vanilla ♪</i>

10:14.530 --> 10:16.240
<i>♪ Ah, ya, ya, ya, ya, ha ♪</i>

10:16.324 --> 10:19.243
<i>♪ I keep on hopin'</i>
<i>We'll eat cake by the ocean ♪</i>

10:19.327 --> 10:20.161
<i>♪ Ah ♪</i>

10:20.244 --> 10:23.664
Yeah! All right, dudes.
We're at the sand! Yeah.

10:26.000 --> 10:28.002
This is my punishment?

10:28.085 --> 10:30.087
This is gonna be
the best summer ever.

10:30.171 --> 10:32.590
All right, you kids have fun. I'm gonna...

10:32.923 --> 10:34.967
Ah, you don't care what I'm gonna do.

10:35.635 --> 10:37.053
Can't wait to get in the water.

10:39.972 --> 10:42.433
We're gonna be lifeguards.
At a real beach.

10:43.017 --> 10:45.978
Did you know you're 100% more likely
to get attacked by an octopus

10:46.062 --> 10:47.605
at a beach than in a pool?

10:47.688 --> 10:48.522
That's a fact.

10:53.152 --> 10:55.488
That's gotta be... a world record.

10:55.863 --> 10:58.783
Uh-oh. I'm goin' down!

10:58.866 --> 10:59.700
I'm okay.

11:01.160 --> 11:02.328
Rode...

11:02.620 --> 11:03.454
bike...

11:03.537 --> 11:04.914
from Valley...

11:04.997 --> 11:06.707
Me.... Eric....

11:07.166 --> 11:09.585
What? That's, like, 20 miles.

11:09.877 --> 11:10.753
Man down!

11:11.545 --> 11:13.714
Eric, you have to keep your feet
elevated.

11:13.798 --> 11:15.633
Helps get the blood back to your brain.

11:15.716 --> 11:17.968
Ew! I just saw up his shorts.

11:19.261 --> 11:21.263
Come on, bro. Come on. All right.

11:21.639 --> 11:24.058
Am I dead? Is this heaven?

11:25.768 --> 11:26.602
Better.

11:27.436 --> 11:28.521
It's Malibu.

11:28.604 --> 11:31.148
- Hey, watch it!
- My bad! Sorry!

11:31.232 --> 11:33.484
Oops! Don't worry, I got it!

11:42.118 --> 11:44.704
Looks like you could use a hand.
I'm Tyler.

11:44.787 --> 11:47.206
Oh, wow, thanks, Tyler. I'm so late.

11:49.500 --> 11:51.669
Looks like you're the one who could
use a hand.

11:52.044 --> 11:53.003
That'd be great.

11:53.087 --> 11:53.921
Wouldn't it?

11:59.593 --> 12:02.179
Jeffy, you seen my great big candy bar?

12:05.391 --> 12:08.602
-Come on. What's that all over your face?
-Don't worry. I'll get that.

12:08.686 --> 12:10.563
Now you're gonna get ants in your mouth.

12:14.150 --> 12:17.903
I think we should set up over there,
because I wanna be close to the water,

12:17.987 --> 12:20.156
but not to need to move
when the tide comes in.

12:20.239 --> 12:23.033
Set up your beach chair?
What are you talking about?

12:23.117 --> 12:27.663
-We're kicking it at the beach all summer!
-Do you even know what Junior Rescue is?

12:28.330 --> 12:29.540
-I do not.

12:34.420 --> 12:37.465
What are you doin' just standin' around,
beach rats?

12:38.090 --> 12:39.675
Aah!

12:39.759 --> 12:42.094
What's up? My name's Brody.

12:42.178 --> 12:43.637
This is my bro, Spencer.

12:43.721 --> 12:46.682
And that is Spencer's bro, Logan,
who is also my bro.

12:47.600 --> 12:48.434
'Sup?

12:48.726 --> 12:52.813
And these are the rest of
the Malibu Beach Junior Rescue Captains.

12:52.897 --> 12:54.982
Over the next two weeks, it is our job

12:55.065 --> 12:58.277
to turn you steaming pile of fish turds
into Junior Rescue.

12:58.611 --> 13:01.238
I thought just by coming here
we're Junior Rescue.

13:01.322 --> 13:03.949
Oh, no. This is the training.

13:04.241 --> 13:05.993
At the end, there's this big test.

13:06.076 --> 13:08.704
We pass that,
then we're actual Junior Rescue.

13:08.788 --> 13:11.207
-Now, we're just fish turds.
-...joy of being captain.

13:11.290 --> 13:15.044
-Then what am I supposed to do with this?
-I'll show you what you can do with this.

13:30.935 --> 13:32.353
Is this a joke to you?

13:32.520 --> 13:35.022
You think this is just
some day at the beach?

13:35.981 --> 13:36.899
Isn't it?

13:39.527 --> 13:42.154
Dude, I'm just messin' around.
Hey, I'm Tyler.

13:42.738 --> 13:45.074
Hi. I'm Eric. Mitchell. Eric Mitchell.

13:45.157 --> 13:46.492
We're from the Valley.

13:47.159 --> 13:48.702
Oh, the Valley.

13:49.453 --> 13:50.871
Oh, well that explains it.

13:50.955 --> 13:52.122
Explains what?

13:52.540 --> 13:53.415
The smell.

13:53.499 --> 13:55.042
That's me!

13:55.125 --> 13:56.961
Rode my bike the whole way here.

13:57.044 --> 13:59.839
And didn't put on deodorant this morning,
'cause I was like,

13:59.922 --> 14:01.590
"We're gettin' in the water anyway!"

14:01.674 --> 14:02.842
Listen up!

14:03.300 --> 14:04.885
You're on my sand now.

14:05.594 --> 14:07.471
I'm gonna run you till you puke.

14:07.847 --> 14:09.598
I'm gonna swim you till you puke.

14:10.140 --> 14:12.059
I'm gonna teach you CPR until you--

14:12.142 --> 14:13.352
-Puke?
-No!

14:14.144 --> 14:18.065
You puke while you're giving CPR, you're
gonna seriously endanger the victim!

14:18.816 --> 14:22.194
Those of you who complete the program
and pass the Crucible

14:22.278 --> 14:26.156
will get to spend the summer working under
actual Malibu lifeguards.

14:27.032 --> 14:30.995
As Senior Captain,
it's my job to make sure you don't suck.

14:31.537 --> 14:32.621
Spencer!

14:32.705 --> 14:34.582
Get these sea slugs
out of my sight.

14:36.417 --> 14:37.543
Two mile run.

14:38.460 --> 14:39.295
Follow me.

14:42.298 --> 14:43.340
Running?

14:43.424 --> 14:45.050
I thought this was gonna be fun.

14:45.134 --> 14:46.719
Move it, Valley!

14:46.802 --> 14:47.928
Before I'm 80!

14:49.096 --> 14:51.056
Hey. Hey! I said follow me!

14:52.349 --> 14:53.350
Get back here!

14:54.184 --> 14:55.936
This is so hardcore!

14:56.020 --> 14:58.063
<i>♪ I need to know, know, know ♪</i>

14:58.147 --> 15:00.524
<i>♪ Whaddaya need, need, need? ♪</i>

15:00.608 --> 15:03.444
<i>♪ Wahddaya like, like, like? ♪</i>

15:03.527 --> 15:05.738
<i>-♪ 'Cause I'm gonna be it tonight ♪</i>

15:05.821 --> 15:08.240
<i>♪ You can be cool, you can be shy ♪</i>

15:08.324 --> 15:10.951
<i>♪ Say what you want, say what you like ♪</i>

15:11.035 --> 15:12.620
<i>♪ 'Cause, ooh, your body talks ♪</i>

15:12.703 --> 15:14.163
-Ha-hem!
<i>-♪ Your body talks ♪</i>

15:14.246 --> 15:15.998
<i>♪ Ooh, ooh, your body talks ♪</i>

15:16.081 --> 15:18.500
<i>♪ You can pretend you don't wanna know ♪</i>

15:18.584 --> 15:21.587
<i>♪ But I read the signs</i>
<i>From your head to your toes ♪</i>

15:22.838 --> 15:24.506
Come on, it's only a half mile!

15:24.590 --> 15:26.675
Put your back into it, Valley!

15:30.512 --> 15:32.514
-Crab in the boat! Crab in the boat!
-Whoa!

15:33.974 --> 15:36.518
How's the 'bu taste, 818?

