15:52.201 --> 15:54.161
<i>♪ 'Cause, ooh, your body talks ♪</i>

15:54.244 --> 15:55.287
<i>♪ Your body talks ♪</i>

15:55.412 --> 15:57.373
<i>♪ Ooh, ooh, your body talks ♪</i>

15:57.456 --> 15:59.792
<i>♪ You can pretend you don't wanna know ♪</i>

15:59.875 --> 16:01.377
Hustle, hustle!

16:02.795 --> 16:04.630
<i>♪ Yeah, you don't need to say a word ♪</i>

