16:25.526 --> 16:27.069
Seven, four...

16:27.152 --> 16:28.278
three...

16:28.362 --> 16:32.324
Okay. Does anyone see a card with a number
two on it? Got a little circle around it?

16:32.616 --> 16:34.952
I told Garvin she wasn't captain material.

16:35.911 --> 16:37.997
Any day now... Dylan.

16:38.580 --> 16:39.623
Right. Um.

